

<br>
Running on Linux
<br>
<br>
Two ways can be used to run the program:
<br>
1. Install or build GStreamer-SDK from <a href="http://docs.gstreamer.com/display/GstSDK/Installing+the+SDK">here</a>.
<br>
2. Install the following packages:
<br>
gtk >= 2 (building: package file from libgtk2.0-dev(with gdk, gdk-pixbuf, glib, gobject, gio))
<br>
gstreamer >= 0.10 (build: libgstreamer0.10-dev)
<br>
gstreamer-interfaces >= 0.10 (dev build: libgstreamer-plugins-base0.10-dev)
<br>
gstreamer-pbutils >= 0.10
<br>
libsoup >= 2.4 (dev bld: libsoup2.4-dev)
<br>
gstreamer-app >= 0.10
<br>
libjpeg-8 (libjpeg8-dev)
<br>
cairo, pango
<br>
libasound2-dev
<br>
Launch the <i>ostream</i> file.
<br>
<br>
Informations about the usage are in <i>info.html</i> and <i>use.html</i>.
<br>
The build was made on Ubuntu 12.04.